<h1 class="hero-h">How to use Claude for market research: <em>methods + prompts.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Market research used to take weeks. With Claude, the work compresses to hours — if you know how to ask. This is the playbook for B2B market research workflows that actually produce decisions, not just decks.</p>
<div class="verdict"><div class="verdict-l">The short version</div><p class="verdict-p">Use Claude for: competitive analysis, ICP refinement, market sizing exercises, trend synthesis from public sources, customer interview analysis. Pair with Perplexity Pro for fresh-source research. Skip dedicated market research platforms unless you need primary research (surveys, interviews). Total cost: $40/month replaces $5K-$30K of analyst time per quarter.</p></div>
</div></div>

<div style="background:#0A1A0A;border-top:1px solid #1A3A1A;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;padding:1.25rem 2.5rem;">
<div style="max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:0.78rem;color:#8FAF8F;">
<div>By <a href="/about" style="color:#F0FFF0;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">Bill Colbert</a> · <span style="color:#4A6A4A;">Founder, Treetop Growth Strategy</span></div>
<div style="color:#4A6A4A;">Published May 2026 · <a href="/content-library" style="color:#8FAF8F;text-decoration:none;">More from the library</a></div>
</div>
